REQUIREMENTS
*	python 2.7
*	python packages ntlk,whoosh, itertools, porterstemmer and text.blob
*	wordnet 3.0

USAGE
create directoy named index/ in your working folder before creating the index
Creating index:
	from  file read.py run create_index(file2, file2)	
file1 and file2 are the english sentence list and its trnslation list aligned parallely

finding closest n matches for a sentence:
from file levenshtein.py run getMatchingSentences(querySentence, number_of_matches, [enableWsd= True])
the third optional argument enables wsd 
